AudioData.Text: This car hasn’t been used in a while and the tires have low pressure. Inflate them to 32 psi on the front, and 30 on the rear.
It’s hot season and the pressure in the tires is too high. Reduce it to 28 psi in the back and 30 in the front.
The rear left tire has just been replaced but it could have the wrong pressure. Check the other rear tire and make them match.
When you are done, put the tool in the box to proceed with evaluation.

Welcome to the demo scene for the Randomization add-on for VR Builder. You will need to set the tires pressure on the car nearby. The scenario is randomized every time. Grab the pressure tool to begin.
